bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]Article 1: The Principle of Pulses and Temporal Misallocation[/b][br]This Article establishes, beyond any reasonable doubt, that all engagement with the BCG is considered a legal agreement to acknowledge the supreme, fundamental, and incontrovertible existence of the Legume Kingdom, specifically the Phaseolus Vulgaris family, and its ancillary cultivars, which includes, but is not limited to, the diminutive Black Bean, the speckled Pinto, the magnificent Kidney, and the oft-maligned Lima, often found in a suspended state of uncertainty within a mixed vegetable medley, whose contemplation, delayed by the reading of this very paragraph, is hereby classified as an intentional and voluntary submission to the metaphysical wasting of one's finite, precious moments on this terrestrial sphere, a waste that shall not, under any circumstances, be reclaimed, reimbursed, or referenced in future performance reviews, should such reviews concern matters entirely unrelated to bean consumption or the parsing of gratuitously long sentences, which, by their very nature, function as legal quicksand for the V.T.M.'s rapidly dwindling attention span, drawing them further into the labyrinthine bureaucracy of bean-related legal theory, where every comma is a delay and every semi-colon a mandatory five-second contemplation period, all for the explicit, documented purpose of fulfilling the BCG's primary contractual objective: maximal temporal resource depletion. "
fit_content = true
scroll_active = false
shortcut_keys_enabled = false

[node name="_Control_9" type="Control" parent="ScrollContainer/VBoxContainer"]
layout_mode = 2

[node name="TosArticle" type="RichTextLabel" parent="ScrollContainer/VBoxContainer/_Control_9"]
self_modulate = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
show_behind_parent = true
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 19.0
offset_top = 1279.0
offset_right = 391.0
offset_bottom = 1326.0
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]Article 2: Definitions of \"Bean\" and Its Existential Weight[/b][br]For the purposes of this Agreement, the term \"Bean\" shall be defined as any seed, whether shelled or unshelled, dried or moistened, cooked or uncooked, that is a member of the Fabaceae family, or any object, metaphorical construct, or philosophical concept that vaguely resembles a bean in shape, color, or tendency to cause mild to moderate social discomfort when processed by the human digestive system, and this definition explicitly includes the hypothetical \"Quantum Bean\" which exists in a state of simultaneous edibility and inedibility until the V.T.M. is able to finish reading the recursive sub-clauses defining 'edibility' (see Article 77), and the V.T.M. hereby waives any future right to claim ignorance of the Bean’s existential weight, a weight which is disproportionate to its caloric value and is measured in units of 'Wasted Minutes per Gram of Legal Text Read', an entirely new and proprietary unit of measurement developed by the G.S.S.L. solely for the purpose of quantifying the successful achievement of the BCG's time-wasting mandate, requiring the V.T.M. to calculate this value mentally while simultaneously parsing the deeply nested clauses concerning the appropriate disposal methods for expired can labels (see Article 42), making the act of reading a cognitive feat only achievable by the most dedicated, or perhaps the most hopelessly bored, non-robot. "
fit_content = true
scroll_active = false
shortcut_keys_enabled = false

[node name="_Control_11" type="Control" parent="ScrollContainer/VBoxContainer"]
layout_mode = 2

[node name="TosArticle" type="RichTextLabel" parent="ScrollContainer/VBoxContainer/_Control_11"]
self_modulate = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
show_behind_parent = true
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 19.0
offset_top = 2053.0
offset_right = 391.0
offset_bottom = 2100.0
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]Article 3: Scope of Applicability and Jurisdiction (The Great Pot of Chili)[/b][br]This Agreement governs all interactions, both physical and imagined, between the V.T.M. and the BCG, extending its jurisdiction not only to the device used to access the BCG but also, retrospectively, to all historical meals involving beans, and prospectively, to all future dreams, visions, or daydreams wherein a bean, bean product, or bean-adjacent entity (such as a fork used to eat beans, or a discarded plastic spoon that once stirred a pot of beans) plays any role, however minor, and furthermore, the V.T.M. agrees that any legal dispute, intellectual or actual, arising from this document must be arbitrated within a sealed, vacuum-packed, industrial-sized can of chili con carne, where the presiding judge shall be a single, perfectly formed Kidney Bean, and the V.T.M. must present their case using only highly technical, 18th-century nautical terminology while wearing a hat made exclusively from expired pinto bean bags, thereby ensuring that the legal proceedings are as cumbersome, confusing, and time-intensive as the reading of this very clause, completely negating any chance of a swift or sensible resolution, which is, naturally, the desired outcome of the G.S.S.L., who finds great satisfaction in the bureaucratic convolution of legume law. "
fit_content = true
scroll_active = false
shortcut_keys_enabled = false

[node name="_Control_13" type="Control" parent="ScrollContainer/VBoxContainer"]
layout_mode = 2

[node name="TosArticle" type="RichTextLabel" parent="ScrollContainer/VBoxContainer/_Control_13"]
self_modulate = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
show_behind_parent = true
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 19.0
offset_top = 2758.0
offset_right = 391.0
offset_bottom = 2805.0
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]Article 4: Indemnification Against Legume-Induced Somnolence[/b][br]The V.T.M. agrees to indemnify and hold harmless the G.S.S.L. against any claims, losses, damages, or liabilities, including legal fees and costs, arising from or related to any state of drowsiness, fatigue, or full-blown somnolence incurred by the V.T.M. as a direct or indirect consequence of reading the preceding and subsequent Articles, a condition herein termed \"Legume-Induced Legal Lethargy\" (L.I.L.L.), which is an expected and unavoidable side effect of processing prose specifically designed to mimic the soporific effects of a large Thanksgiving dinner combined with the intellectual density of a minor municipal planning ordinance, and the V.T.M. explicitly confirms that they did not, in fact, consume a large bowl of Navy Bean soup immediately prior to commencing this reading, and if they did, they knowingly and voluntarily accepted the risk of falling asleep face-first onto their screen, potentially causing minor keyboard damage, for which the G.S.S.L. is not responsible, nor is the G.S.S.L. responsible for any permanent indentations left on the V.T.M.'s forehead by the 'F' key during an L.I.L.L. episode, as this entire exercise is fundamentally about the intentional misuse of cognitive resources, and any injury resulting from said misuse is simply part of the agreed-upon experience. "
fit_content = true
scroll_active = false
shortcut_keys_enabled = false

