text = "[b]Article 21: Compliance Regarding the Adzuki Bean (The Minor Pulse)[/b][br]The V.T.M. must agree to treat the Adzuki Bean with the same reverence and attention as larger, more culturally dominant pulses, and failure to acknowledge its subtle, sweet undertones in any mental or verbal discourse shall be deemed an act of 'Leguminous Neglect' (L.N.), punishable by a mandatory self-correction exercise requiring the V.T.M. to spend three minutes meditating solely on the Adzuki Bean's historical significance in Japanese confectionery, a period of forced contemplation designed to be just long enough to break the V.T.M.'s reading rhythm and force them to re-establish their concentration, further draining their limited supply of patience and free time, which is the entire point of this incredibly long and deliberately tedious legal text. "
