text = "[b]Article 22: The Temporal Distortion Field of the Speckled Cranberry Bean[/b][br]The Cranberry Bean, due to its mottled, painterly appearance, is scientifically proven to generate a minor 'Temporal Distortion Field' (T.D.F.) when viewed for longer than six seconds, and the V.T.M. is hereby warned that any prolonged viewing of the Cranberry Bean may result in the V.T.M. perceiving the remaining articles of this Agreement as being even longer than they actually are, a psychological trick that the G.S.S.L. is not only aware of but actively encourages, as the goal is to induce a feeling of endless, inescapable bureaucratic entanglement, maximizing the sensation of wasted time, and the V.T.M. cannot sue for emotional damages resulting from this T.D.F., as the warning is explicitly contained within this ridiculously long sentence that they have now successfully parsed, demonstrating their (perhaps foolish) commitment to continuing this reading exercise. "
