text = "[b]Article 24: The Mung Bean's Status as an 'Emergent' Pulse[/b][br]The Mung Bean, often encountered in its sprouted form, holds the status of an 'Emergent Leguminous Entity' (E.L.E.), and the V.T.M. must dedicate at least 90 seconds of silent reflection on the process of germination, focusing specifically on the energy expenditure required to break the seed coat, an exercise that is mandatory before proceeding, and this is yet another transparent attempt by the G.S.S.L. to force a non-essential pause in the reading, ensuring that the V.T.M. loses momentum and spends a significant, yet entirely pointless, chunk of time contemplating seed biology rather than efficiently completing the Captcha requirement, a testament to the document's unwavering commitment to the systematic eradication of productivity. "
