text = "[b]Article 25: The Runner Bean's Right to Vertical Growth[/b][br]The V.T.M. must acknowledge the Runner Bean's unique, non-bush-like growth habit and its inherent right to verticality, and any mental image of the Runner Bean growing horizontally shall be considered a philosophical affront to its biological mandate, requiring the V.T.M. to immediately visualize a trellised, perfectly vertical Runner Bean vine, complete with tiny, miniature safety harnesses and ropes, for exactly 30 seconds, a visualization exercise designed to be detailed, specific, and mentally taxing, ensuring that the V.T.M.'s brain power is diverted toward highly specific, entirely useless agricultural fantasy, thereby achieving the desired state of maximum temporal and cognitive misallocation, which is the singular, overarching goal of this entire, nonsensical legal agreement. "
