bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]Article 44: Prohibition on Comparing Beans to Coffee or Cocoa[/b][br]The V.T.M. is strictly prohibited from making any comparative references between beans and the seeds of the coffee or cocoa plant, as this form of 'Caffeine-Induced Legume Envy' (C.I.L.E.) is deemed an insult to the bean's humble, non-stimulatory nature, and any internal mental comparison will result in a penalty requiring the V.T.M. to immediately re-read Articles 1 through 10, thereby guaranteeing an absolute, measurable doubling of their wasted time and reinforcing the core concept that compliance with this agreement is intentionally punitive and absurdly time-consuming. "
