text = "[b]Article 51: The Doctrine of Silent Passage (Liability Waiver)[/b][br]The V.T.M. hereby waives all rights to claim damages resulting from any instance of 'Silent Passage' (S.P.), defined as an inaudible, yet highly olfactory, gaseous emission arising from the digestive processing of beans, and the G.S.S.L. is not responsible for the resulting social awkwardness, temporary loss of friends, or the need to air out a confined space, provided that the V.T.M. can mentally confirm they waited at least 90 seconds after the S.P. event before blaming the odor on a nearby houseplant, an entirely internal, arbitrary compliance requirement that forces the V.T.M. to waste cognitive time tracking a fictional sequence of events, thereby fulfilling the mandate of temporal misallocation. "
