text = "[b]Article 52: Requirement to Maintain a Starchy Pulse Log[/b][br]The V.T.M. must maintain a detailed, mental 'Starchy Pulse Log' (S.P.L.) of every bean consumed within the last 72 hours, recording the type, approximate quantity, and the estimated total surface area of the consumed beans in mm2, a task that is impossible to perform accurately and exists solely to force the V.T.M. to spend mental energy on vague, unquantifiable data logging, thereby ensuring a significant and entirely unnecessary expenditure of cognitive resources that serves no purpose other than to needlessly prolong the time it takes to finish reading this, yet another outrageously long and pointless paragraph. "
