text = "[b]Article 54: Non-Transferability of Bean-Induced Euphoria[/b][br]Any temporary feeling of well-being, satisfaction, or mild, bean-induced euphoria (B.I.E.) experienced by the V.T.M. after a particularly delicious meal shall be non-transferable and may not be leveraged as collateral for any future loan, service, or favor, and the V.T.M. must mentally file a 'B.I.E. Non-Transfer Notice' (B.N.T.N.) with the imaginary D.G.L.C. (see Article 6), a pointless, internal bureaucratic step designed solely to interrupt the reading flow and ensure that the V.T.M. spends valuable seconds on a completely fictional legal formality. "
