text = "[b]Article 60: The Bean's Right to be Heard (Acoustic Compliance)[/b][br]The V.T.M. must ensure that any bean consumed is granted a momentary 'Acoustic Compliance' period, where the V.T.M. must mentally listen for the subtle, internal 'squish' or 'pop' of the bean as it is masticated, and failure to acknowledge this subtle sound will result in a penalty requiring the V.T.M. to immediately write a three-line poem about the sound of a bean being chewed, thereby adding a layer of compulsory, arbitrary creative endeavor to the already dense layer of compulsory, arbitrary legal interpretation. "
