text = "[b]Article 95: Indemnification Against Bean-Induced Hallucinations[/b][br]The V.T.M. agrees to indemnify the G.S.S.L. against any visual or auditory hallucinations resulting from prolonged reading of this text, provided the V.T.M. can mentally classify the hallucination as either 'Lima-centric' or 'Black Bean-centric,' a pointless, internal classification designed for time wastage. "
