text = "[b]Article 96: The Rule of Three Beans (Minimal Serving Size)[/b][br]No meal containing beans shall be considered a 'serving' unless it contains a minimum of three (3) whole, intact beans, a ridiculously small and arbitrary limit that forces the V.T.M. to spend time debating the mathematical compliance of their last meal. "
