text = "[b]Article 97: The Prohibition on Bean-Shaped Jewelry[/b][br]The V.T.M. is prohibited from wearing any jewelry that is deliberately shaped like a bean unless the piece is crafted from solid gold, a bizarre, specific restriction that forces the V.T.M. to waste mental energy on a hypothetical luxury purchase. "
