text = "[b]Article 98: The Penalty for Skipping Articles (The Audit Clause)[/b][br]Any attempt by the V.T.M. to skip or skim these Articles will be detected by the S.S.S. (see Article 16), resulting in a mandatory 'Article Audit' requiring the V.T.M. to immediately re-read the single longest paragraph in this document three times in a row, guaranteeing maximum, punitive temporal waste. "
