text = "[b]Article 99: Full Acceptance of Temporal Misallocation[/b][br]By reading this far, the V.T.M. confirms their absolute and irrevocable acceptance that the entire purpose of this document was to waste their time, and that this successful, deliberate temporal misallocation is the true, binding contract, superseding all other clauses, and the V.T.M. is now contractually obligated to spend 60 seconds reflecting on the irony of their situation. "
